Given the constraint of C# version 6 or less, your web view component is almost certainly an older one, likely based on Internet Explorer. This means we must completely avoid modern CSS properties that are not supported by that engine, such as backdrop-filter, grid, and some more advanced flexbox features.
The original CSS you provided was already quite good and used a responsive approach with float and media queries, which is perfect for this situation. I've refactored your code to remove the unsupported backdrop-filter property and made sure all other properties are widely compatible with older browsers. The "frosted glass" effect will be replaced with a simple, semi-transparent white background, which is the standard and safest fallback.
Here is the complete and robust CSS code, fully compatible with older C# web views and responsive for different screen sizes.
/* Global Styles for Body */
body {
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #e0ecf8, #f8fbff); /* Soft blue gradient */
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    color: #1a202c;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 20px;
    background-attachment: fixed;
    background-size: cover;
}

/* Main Container - Fallback for older browsers */
.passenger-container {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 30px;
    /* Replaced backdrop-filter with a solid, semi-transparent background */
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

/* Card Styling */
.passenger-card {
    /* Used a solid semi-transparent color for consistency with the main container */
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    padding: 35px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    transition: transform 0.3s;
}

.passenger-card:hover {
    transform: scale(1.01);
}

/* Heading Styles */
h2.passenger-title {
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #2a4365;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
    font-size: 2rem;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    position: relative;
}

h2.passenger-title::before {
    content: "‚úàÔ∏è ";
    font-size: 1.5rem;
}

.passenger-card h5 {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #4a5568;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
}

.passenger-card h5::before {
    content: "üìù ";
}

/* Column Layout using floats for responsiveness */
.row::after {
    content: "";
    display: table;
    clear: both;
}

.col-md-3, .col-md-4, .col-md-6 {
    float: left;
    padding: 0 15px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.col-md-3 { width: 25%; }
.col-md-4 { width: 33.3333%; }
.col-md-6 { width: 50%; }

/* Responsive for Mobile */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .col-md-3, .col-md-4, .col-md-6 {
        width: 100%;
        float: none;
        padding: 0;
    }
}

/* Labels and Inputs */
.passenger-label {
    display: block;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #718096;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.passenger-input, .passenger-select {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background-color: #f7fafc;
    color: #2d3748;
    transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
    font-size: 1rem;
    box-shadow: inset 0 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
}

.passenger-input:focus, .passenger-select:focus {
    border-color: #4299e1;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(66, 153, 225, 0.3);
    background-color: #fff;
    outline: none;
}

.passenger-input[readonly], .passenger-select[readonly] {
    background-color: #edf2f7;
    cursor: not-allowed;
}

/* Buttons */
.passenger-btn-primary {
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #4299e1, #3182ce);
    color: white;
    border: none;
    padding: 14px 30px;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    border-radius: 10px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.passenger-btn-primary:hover {
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #2b6cb0, #2c5282);
}

.passenger-btn-secondary {
    background: #a0aec0;
    color: white;
    border: none;
    padding: 14px 30px;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    border-radius: 10px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    margin-right: 10px;
}

.passenger-btn-secondary:hover {
    background-color: #718096;
}

/* Spacing */
